"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?26/13/26841/abstract/6\">",
"      Khair K, Liesner R. Bruising and bleeding in infants and children--a practical approach. Br J Haematol 2006; 133:221.",
"     </a>",
